{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ABOUT THE GAME</h2><br>You are Landon \u2014 trapped in a twisted and terrifying dream, wondering a mysterious old house. Warm memories and terrible realities are intertwined and tragedy unfolds as you explore, find clues and solve puzzles in this long-forgotten nightmare.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/GIF_01_Steam.gif?t=1688115863\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MAIN FEATURES</h2><br>\u25fc A rich environment with atmospheric music and SFX for horror immersion<br>\u25fc Puzzles and hidden clues with moderate difficulty<br>\u25fc Terrifying animations and events; including some gore<br>\u25fc High-quality Chinese VO for an authentic Chinese horror experience<br>\u25fc Fully localised subtitles, UI and voiceovers<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/GIF_02_Steam.gif?t=1688115863\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY FEATURE</h2><br>Delve deep into your own inner world, confront the horrible truth about the tragic deaths of Lilith and her family. Your goal is to uncover a hidden conspiracy; the blood and sin that\u2019s fuelled the success of an infamous cult known as Saint Cohen. A cruel sacrifice awaits you; the chains of flesh are foretelling your fate. With no way out, do you accept the fate or fight against it?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/GIF_05_Steam.gif?t=1688115863\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">VR FEATURES</h2><br>\u25fc Supports HTC VIVE, Oculus Quest, Valve Index<br>\u25fc Improved VR movement with six degrees of freedom (6DOF)<br>\u25fc Full locomotion with snap-turning rotation<br>\u25fc Packed with interactive items; pick up, discard, knock or destroy<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1487450/extras/GIF_03_Steam.gif?